ZH: 过江之鲫，其势美也。
EN: The crossing-river carp displays its beauty in the current.

ZH: 过江之鲫，身姿矫健。
EN: The crossing-river carp has a graceful figure.

ZH: 过江之鲫，波涛之上逍遥自在。
EN: The crossing-river carp swims freely on the turbulent waves.

ZH: 过江之鲫，不惧风浪。
EN: The crossing-river carp is not afraid of the wind and waves.

ZH: 过江之鲫，追逐着阳光。
EN: The crossing-river carp chases after the sunlight.

ZH: 过江之鲫，独具风采。
EN: The crossing-river carp has its own charm.

ZH: 过江之鲫，挑战可能的极限。
EN: The crossing-river carp challenges the possible limits.

ZH: 过江之鲫，顶天立地。
EN: The crossing-river carp stands tall.

ZH: 过江之鲫，含笑九泉。
EN: The crossing-river carp smiles in the nine springs.

ZH: 过江之鲫，无惧颠簸颠翻。
EN: The crossing-river carp is not afraid of rough waters.

ZH: 过江之鲫，心广如海。
EN: The crossing-river carp has a heart as broad as the sea.

ZH: 过江之鲫，包容一切。
EN: The crossing-river carp is inclusive of everything.

ZH: 过江之鲫，不愁起落。
EN: The crossing-river carp does not worry about ups and downs.

ZH: 过江之鲫，潜心修行。
EN: The crossing-river carp focuses on self-cultivation.

ZH: 过江之鲫，一路高歌。
EN: The crossing-river carp sings along the way.

ZH: 过江之鲫，隐忍自若。
EN: The crossing-river carp hides its true feelings calmly.

ZH: 过江之鲫，坚定无比。
EN: The crossing-river carp is extremely determined.

ZH: 过江之鲫，不输人间。
EN: The crossing-river carp does not lose to the world.

ZH: 过江之鲫，心灵如水。
EN: The crossing-river carp has a soul as calm as water.

ZH: 过江之鲫，永不气馁。
EN: The crossing-river carp never gives up.
